column5: Thanks for your comment most appreciated swung too late was from a song Fireflies by Marie Hines it means that I tried to live too late in my life. As for Deadpool 2 everybody needs someone to belong to is the whole gist of that movie which is one of the best movies even  as raunchy as it is. It's one of the best movies best meaning Picture Shows that I've seen in years highly recommended. PEACE to you and God Bless.

Thank you for the comment most appreciated. I've been watching Deadpool 2 like 6 or 7 x and that whole entire movie I can relate to being where I am this latest stage of life I swung too late. And I don't have any hope left especially for myself. Peace to you God bless merry Christmas and happy New Year.

I feel you girl fuckem.! I don't know what to say other than I'm hurting too that's f***** up Christmas season ain't going to be any better being alone and isolated no friends no family no reason to breathe it just sucks. But that doesn't have to be you you can find someone somewhere they'll listen and talk I understand how you're hurting cuz I'm hurting too God bless take care peace to you.

Well at least you're honest that's a good quality. Stay in school stay focused it'll help with insanity. I'm just as insane but at 50 don't have anything to show for it so at least can you get a good degree you'll have something to show for your insanity. But unfortunately I don't date tall women. Peace to you girl God bless Merry Christmas.
